Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: soc-acpi: introduce new 'machine check' callback
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: dcf4694f200a67784e053eb5d1d70a191761ff4f
